race.description: Club Hotel Country Cup Qualifier/ Roma Cup
race.comment: TIJUANA TWO STEP (5) raced in the leading division and kept going to score by 2.5 lengths last time out over 1070m at Chinchilla. Drawn to stalk the leaders. Stepping up a level this time but on her best form she is one of the key runners. DECIDUOUS (6) was a narrow winner by half a length at Charleville two back then second there last time. Down in the weights on the last run. Goes very well at this journey, boasting two wins from four starts and shapes as a key contender. I AM GOOD AT THIS (11) is racing well in lower company recently and while he has to make the jump in grade, he drops in weight. Can feature. SCORCHED LAND (10) hasn't been far away in recent efforts and is worth plenty of thought.
